Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:04.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Dr. Sheldon Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:10.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And welcome to Sheldon Cooper Presents: Fun with Flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the Final Episode Flagtacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was coming. Still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm sure you're thinking, "The final episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,who will stand between us and flag ignorance"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a show on flags or mind reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:34.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is I can no longer balance a full-time career,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,a popular Internet show, and a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And he really does have one, you jerks on the comment board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:45.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So as they say, all good things must come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After only 232 episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,233 if we include the one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:54.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,somebody forgot to press record on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you weren't gonna bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said you pressed record.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please sit back, relax,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and join us as we take our final lap...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...as indicated by the waving of this racing flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:12.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,有些代表场上有慢速车辆  有些则是最后一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, of course, white flags can also represent surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the Stewards of Gondor, and the Japanese Minamoto clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:18.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,日本源氏与平家大战时  一家白旗  一家红旗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you remember that from episode 62,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"White Flags: Who's Wavin' 'Em and Why""
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I thought cleaning out a dead professor's office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,was gonna just be boring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but then I found his dentures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and realized it's also gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Professor Abbott's family want any of this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's rough. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can spend your whole life working,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:18.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and at the end all that's left are some papers in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey, we're supposed to look through all this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,before we throw it away in case it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did. It's all outdated or disproved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. This old pen kind of proves gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:37.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tilt it, her bathing suit falls right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my dad used to have a pen like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I dated it all through sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:44.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It still feels weird
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,just throwing away his work like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, someone will be throwing out your work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:55.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That someone was Sheldon, and the day was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Roger, to be opened upon your first great discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:09.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved this 50 years and never got to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Roger Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger Abbott sounds just like Roger Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger Abbott, Roger Abbott, Roger Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God, Leonard, I know he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but try it. It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger Abbott, Roger Rabbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my rookie of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dan. My boss who didn't want to hire me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and now's a little hug machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at you. Brand-new and already the third best sales rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why don't you come over to my table. - Yes. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bernadette's just parking the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bernadette. Cute, sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,vicious little Bernadette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. She's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,At the company picnic she yelled at me and my grandson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,for losing the three-legged race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:08.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he still calls her "That mean kid with the big boobies."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she can be a little intense, but, I swear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,she is so sweet once you get past all the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking about how much we love working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the years here at Fun With Flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we've had an opportunity to learn, laugh, wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, yes, even shed a tear or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:37.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you do a two-hour Fourth of July spectacular
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and it doesn't get recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to say I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How about 4,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One for every domino I set up to make that American flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy these highlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Crikey! What flag do we have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Australia, mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:12.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's time for the speed round of Flag or Not a Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Flag. Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a flag. Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am crushing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Betsy Ross, what you working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,但缺乏足够的档案记载以佐证这一观点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the story of me sewing the first American flag
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is unsupported poppycock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did sew it, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a simple seamstress whose descendants are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,out to make a quick buck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy a dip, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that purple flag indicates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that marine pests, such as jellyfish, are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that flag is a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:10.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a flag. Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Flag. Not a flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When stuff like this gets me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,you know what I like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing "Hakuna Matata" Like an eight-year-old girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,意为"不用担心"或"没有问题"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, smarty-pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Everything Is Awesome" From The Lego Movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're full of pages and pages of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He clearly spent years on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just columns of random numbers. Toss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but what if this was a potential breakthrough for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What if... what if this is the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that would've finally let him open that bottle of champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he didn't know what to pair champagne with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:03.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberries, caviar, oysters. All good choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that look right there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is why people eat before they come to your parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no discernible pattern that I can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but it shouldn't be too hard to run the numbers and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we can get some time on the supercomputer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. We could try multiple regressions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with varying physical and experimental constants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we could run a pattern-matching algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,against well-known unsolved physics problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it might be a substitution cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We could start with basic cryptanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or we could talk to this guy he used to share an office with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't know how to do cryptanalysis, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure if it's the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Dan, you have a grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How old is he? - Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I remember him from the picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one crying like a wuss the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was being picked on by a mean kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just builds character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like my dad said, "Nobody likes a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,except their mommies and Democrats."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need another drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Maybe he didn't like the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that you called his grandson a wuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't think you were supposed to say "sissy" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, look, I know what a good person you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but sometimes people think you might come off a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, like, the sweetest person I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me. I should be in a tree baking cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,people think you're a little mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You one of those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think the cookie thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Action.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest today is a returning fan favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He puts the reading in your rainbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the Geordi in your La Forge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Kunta in your Kinte,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. LeVar Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sheldon. Now, remember our deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:28.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You do this, I delete your contact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,While...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,While you watch me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Happy to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to get your opinion on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In honor of Black History Month,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I portrayed George Washington Carver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,对美国有十分大贡献的一名黑人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:47.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in a loving tribute that my roommate called "wildly racist"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. My name is George.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him, Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not racist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we sure this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The doorman said this is the right building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if you're pulling up your pants,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not a doorman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm looking for a Professor Sharpe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can I help you? - Hi. We're from the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to get some information about Professor Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We were cleaning out his office
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and found these books full of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Any chance you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was always working on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it might be some sort of interstellar coordinate system,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe an updated version of Hubble's law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep seeing the number 90 repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be the angle of perturbation of a distant galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the number of calories in a yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his food diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he wrote down everything he ever ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was convinced that calorie restriction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,was the key to living forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he could have been hit by a bus. You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's not more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On the bright side, you didn't have to listen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to his stomach growl for 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was there anything that Professor Abbott worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,during his life that came close to an accomplishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, his research never amounted to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You were his colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your research turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:28.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is the apartment you get when you win a Nobel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could be very frugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a little tired of everybody's sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, maybe I come off a little strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's only because my dad raised me to be tough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and not to take crap from anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a difference between being tough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and telling your friend her new pants
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,look like a saggy diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I did say that, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so self-conscious, I had to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? To Babies R Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry. Can we just go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like everybody hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, they don't hate you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just a little intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is show everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,how sweet you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I think I'd rather go. - No, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not going anywhere, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here for you, and we are gonna fix this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though your dress is ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my little Flag-keteers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like the last episode of Fun with Flags is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:39.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I would run each and every one of you viewers up a flagpole
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:40.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是试试水  看看反应的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and salute you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you touched the ground, burn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,如果国旗被弄脏或要退役  得庄重处理  通常烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to personally thank Dr. Amy Farrah Fowler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,who you may or may not know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is the first woman to co-host a flag
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:58.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,or banner-related Internet info-tainment show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, glass ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I may get serious for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,hosting this show has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,one crazy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,With all its ups and downs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't give it up for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for now, when I'm giving it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I sign off, I'd, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:33.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to share with you all one last use for a white flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheldon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't press record...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I pressed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the end of Roger Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And we still don't know who framed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I still keep thinking about how an entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,can seemingly amount to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the sad truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:21.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,not everyone will accomplish something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us may just have to find meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:28.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in the little moments that make up life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah for you, not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to space. I'm covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This bottle was meant to celebrate an achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When one of us gets their first big breakthrough,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll celebrate by opening this bottle of champagne
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and toasting Professor Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,rubbing our success in Sheldon's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, well, that's the best part. - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan, could I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just want you to know I didn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to be rude about your grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Penny told me that everyone's scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know she drinks, right? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's right, and I just want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that from now on, I'm gonna be much more sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone walking on eggshells around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, okay, then, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,one thing I've been meaning to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:39.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is that the company is gonna stop paying for our coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. When does that start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?! - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's been paying for my coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It comes from the swear jar
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we put money in when you curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What else don't I know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Uh, well, you know your private bathroom? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That was supposed to be for the whole floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're kidding. - No, no. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It only really affected wheelchair Kathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's back in the hospital now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,so it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, maybe you shouldn't have named her "Wheelchair Kathy."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everybody liked me, but I'm just a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:26.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But a cute one, like that, uh, eyeball guy in Monsters, Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't cry. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I even work here anymore? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Because this company needs you. - It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mind paying for the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could get you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,an espresso machine for your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I guess that would be all right. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You don't have to be mean to get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:00.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where did we land on my bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're up so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:12.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I posted the last episode of Fun with Flags hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and not a single person cared enough to comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All that effort for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the day throwing out a man's entire career,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and all that's left is an old bottle of champagne
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and a naked lady pen that Raj took
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,when he thought no one was looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you know how I feel at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You do get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone left a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Too bad your show is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of liked it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:58.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the people are heartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this away from the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun with Flags is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheldon, that wasn't for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm not going to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hear the pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew it was coming. Still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,LeVar Burton?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,LeVar Burton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,LeVar Burton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to call,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and I didn't know how else to give you the good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun with Flags is back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can be in the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wil Wheaton said, get a gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't know why I didn't get a gate. - You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,At least listen to the premise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were born in Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could talk about German flags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:06.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about dressing up like a swastika?
